This patch integrates MountZero VFS into the kernel tree.
Apply after SUSFS v2.1.0 patches.

Steps:
1. Copy source_files/ to kernel tree
2. Update fs/Makefile: obj-$(CONFIG_MOUNTZERO) += mountzero.o mountzero_vfs.o
3. Update fs/Kconfig: Add CONFIG_MOUNTZERO entry
4. Hook into fs/namei.c: mountzero_vfs_getname_hook()
